{"tid":2493454,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"20年前工程收分要2條A，Poly三寶先2條C","createTime":"2021-04-18T02:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T02:59:39.000Z","uid":69836,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb6b7e2bdf7b47afe8f7b432113c353c6ff8333","tid":2493454,"uid":69836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:34:08.000Z","msg":"20年前嘅工程<br />\n<a href=\"http://web2.education18.com/hkedrequire/hkedrequire_2001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb2.education18.com%2Fhkedrequire%2Fhkedrequire_2001.html&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=cc94f878\" target=\"_blank\">http://web2.education18.com/hkedrequire/hkedrequire_2001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n依家就調轉<br />\nPoly 三寶個個爭住入, 冇2個5**都未必入到<br />\n工程就水泡<br />\n<br />\n20年前入行嘅工程同學仔應該都上曬associated director/technical director<br />\n人工<strong>至少</strong>每月8-10萬<br />\n20年前入行3寶, 依家可能做緊senior , 唔計自己開鋪, <strong>頂薪</strong>8萬<br />\n<br />\n不過, 工程一定係辛苦啲"},{"pid":"a136e6bb284c6997f827411ff08cbc35cf9007ea","tid":2493454,"uid":69836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"20年後<br />\n即係依家<br />\n會唔會風水輪流轉?<br />\n<br />\n工程變返神科<br />\n三寶變返係人都入到<br />\n<br />\n依家東華, 明愛, OU, 都可以比DSE分數唔理想既同學讀到三寶<br />\n畢業人數上升<br />\nkeep住咁樣5-10年<br />\n理論上係可以拉低返Poly三寶個收分分數<br />\n<br />\n但至於工程就................<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce080d52f3a591693b0a8501a6f73da53617b9d9","tid":2493454,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"20年前果批撞正03年收晒皮啦"},{"pid":"dbf37e3c2955cf73e715af5a2503ca587ddee8a7","tid":2493454,"uid":69836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:41:54.000Z","msg":"老實說<br />\n依家世界大趨勢係AI, 科技領先<br />\n可惜既係香港唔太重視<br />\n但如果眼光望遠少少<br />\n係香港讀完工程, 去外國發展, 係一個幾唔錯嘅選擇黎"},{"pid":"1e5305d004f52a9d1a0f966f012fb6748744dfc9","tid":2493454,"uid":24715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"